name: [FRAME 04] The Brain of Charles Nelson Reilly
description: Part four of the [FRAME] series depicts the rotating brain of actor and celebrity Match Game panel member Charles Nelson Reilly. Here it waits, preserved in ones and zeroes, for the day he can be brought back to life to amuse us with his antics once more. 640x490 pixels, 11.64 MB, 80 frames.
